icons/statuses/resolved.png","name":"Resolved","id":"5","statusCategory":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/statuscategory/3","id":3,"key":"done","colorName":"green","name":"Done"}},"components":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/10005","id":"10005","name":"DNS"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/component/12700","id":"12700","name":"OSG","description":"Object Storage Gateway"}],"timeoriginalestimate":null,"customfield_13000":null,"description":"h2. Problem\r\n\r\nWe are currently unable to access objects within an S3 bucket using CNAME records.  We want to be able to access the file located at the following url:\r\n{noformat}http://mybucket.mydomain.com.objectstorage.eucadomain.mydomain.com/myfile.txt{noformat}\r\nwith the following CNAME:\r\n{noformat}http://mybucket.mydomain.com/myfile.txt{noformat}\r\n\r\nThey key advantage is being able to drop the {{objectstorage.eucadomain}} from the URL and access the file with a cleaner URL.\r\n\r\nh2. Steps to reproduce.\r\n\r\n# Upload the file {{myfile.txt}} to the bucket {{mybucket.mydomain.com}}\r\n# Create the CNAME record on the external DNS server\r\n{noformat}\r\nmybucket.mydomain.com   CNAME        mybucket.mydomain.com.objectstorage.eucadomain.mydomain.com.{noformat}\r\n# Download the file using the full URL\r\n{noformat}\r\n# curl http://mybucket.mydomain.com.objectstorage.eucadomain.mydomain.com/myfile.txt\r\nThis is a test document.\r\n{noformat}\r\n# Download the file using the CNAME\r\n{noformat}\r\n# curl http://mybucket.mydomain.com/myfile.txt\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\"?><Response><Errors><Error><Code>404 Not Found</Code><Message>unknown</Message></Error></Errors><RequestID>unknown</RequestID></Response>\r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\nh2. Workaround\r\n\r\nNone currently.\r\n\r\n(!)*NOTE*: This was tested with many combinations of bucket names and CNAME records (i.e. bucket name was {{mybucket}} rather than {{mybucket.mydomain.com}})\r\n\r\nh2. References\r\n\r\nAmazon's documentation on how to configure buckets for use with CNAMEs:\r\nhttp://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/dev/VirtualHosting.html#VirtualHostingCustomURLs","customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":null,"customfield_11500":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=lincoln.thomas","name":"lincoln.thomas","key":"lincoln.thomas","accountId":"557058:f9364c00-87ee-4948-b657-bb8f8f2030ea","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c21bba9797b880c34a5d772e6db4664f?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dlincoln.thomas%26avatarId%3D17800%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c21bba9797b880c34a5d772e6db4664f?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dlincoln.thomas%26avatarId%3D17800%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c21bba9797b880c34a5d772e6db4664f?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dlincoln.thomas%26avatarId%3D17800%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c21bba9797b880c34a5d772e6db4664f?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dlincoln.thomas%26avatarId%3D17800%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Lincoln Thomas","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"timetracking":{},"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"attachment":[],"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"summary":"S3 CNAME virtual hosting support for buckets","creator":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=jgallucci32","name":"jgallucci32","key":"jgallucci32","accountId":"557058:1cd98ee4-b2ee-4683-a315-2a6abd75b048","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/31cfdf964a6ac26962c22f3279e2c85c?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D1012